 This install applies to "Stunt Car Racer" © 1989 Geoff Crammond/Microstyle.
 Framerate Unleashed modification by Vesuri/dA JoRMaS.

 Requirements:
 -------------
 This install requires WHDLoad version 17.0 and DIC to be in the path.
 These programs can be found in the WHDLoad package.
 To install from a different drive than DF0: select installation mode Expert.

 The installed program requires 0.5 MB ChipMem and 0.5 MB fast memory.
 A fast CPU (68020 or better) is required for the improved framerate to be
 of any benefit. The game will run on an Amiga 500 but the framerate will
 not be improved.
 The game can be quit by pressing F10 (key can be changed with Tooltype
 "QuitKey=").

 Features:
 ---------
 This modification unlocks the framerate of Stunt Car Racer without
 modifying the speed or the physics of the game.

 Two slave files are provided:
   StuntCarRacer.slave   - PAL version, 50 FPS
   StuntTrackRacer.slave - NTSC version, 60 FPS (title: Stunt Track Racer)

 Both slaves support the following tooltypes:
   C1: Toggle infinite boost (F6)
   C2: The New Tracks - enables the Stunt Car Racer TNT hack version

 Known limitations:
 ------------------
 - Computer link play via serial cable is not supported.
 - The original game code has not been optimized; there is likely room for
   further performance improvement.

